The paper discusses the development of intelligent machines, which is a core topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The focus on communication and learning suggests that the paper could also belong to the sub-categories of natural language processing (cs.CL) and machine learning (cs.LG). The proposed environment for teaching the machine suggests that the paper could also be relevant to robotics (cs.RO) and systems and control (cs.SY).
